  "instructions": [
    "Rinse the iceberg lettuce under cold water, pat dry, and chop into bite-size pieces.",
    "In a mixing bowl, combine the diced avocado, halved cherry tomatoes, and sliced red onion, then toss gently.",
    "Spread the chopped lettuce into a large bowl and fold in the avocado mixture.",
    "Add the roasted chickpeas, sprinkle the smoked paprika, sea salt, and black pepper, then toss to coat evenly.",
    "Drizzle the olive oil and fresh lime juice over the salad, stirring until the greens are lightly coated.",
    "Sprinkle chopped cilantro over the top for a fresh herbal note.",
    "Drizzle the lacquer glaze over the salad, letting it pool slightly on the surface.",
    "Serve immediately, allowing the glaze to give a subtle glossy finish."
  ],
